---
const artist = {
    name: "Farewell Blu",
    photo: "/images/epk/farewellblu-1.jpg",
    achievements: [
        "Opened for Sadgirl",
        "Featured on KROK, CSFU, CSLB Radio",
        "Over 50k streams on Spotify",
        "Soundtracked short film *Neon Grief*",
    ],
    contact: {
        email: "mgmt@gargylonrecords.com",
        instagram: "https://instagram.com/farewellblu",
        handle: "@farewellblu",
    },
    song: {
        title: "I Should Be Out Dancing",
        spotifyEmbed: "https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3sixe55jEQIkvX4bBFfGT7?utm_source=generator"
    }
};

---

<style>
    :root {
        --accent: #8b0000;
        --bg: #000000;
        --text: antiquewhite;
    }

    body {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "Palatino Linotype", serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .hero-logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .logo-gif {
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 80%;
        height: auto;
    }


    .photo-bio {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .photo-bio {
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
    }

    .photo-bio img {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 400px;
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .bio {
        flex: 1;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .bio p {
        margin-top: 0;
        text-indent: 1.5em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    }


    h2 {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-weight: normal;
    }

    ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
    }

    iframe {
        display: block;
        margin: 1rem auto;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .contact {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    a {
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    .split-section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .split-section {
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .split-section > div {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .split-section .achievements {
            padding-right: 2rem;
        }

        .split-section .music {
            padding-left: 2rem;
        }
    }

    .achievements ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    .music iframe {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .tagline {
        text-align: center;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #bbb;
        margin-top: -3rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .image-swap {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 400px;
        aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .img {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .base {
        z-index: 0;
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .img-2,
    .img-3,
    .img-4 {
        opacity: 0;
    }

    .image-swap:hover .img-2,
    .image-swap:hover .img-3,
    .image-swap:hover .img-4 {
        opacity: 0; /* default hide unless specific zone is hovered */
    }

    .hover-zone {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 25%;
        left: 0;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .zone-1 {
        top: 0;
    }
    .zone-2 {
        top: 25%;
    }
    .zone-3 {
        top: 50%;
    }
    .zone-4 {
        top: 75%;
    }

    .zone-1:hover ~ .img-2 { opacity: 1; }
    .zone-2:hover ~ .img-3 { opacity: 1; }
    .zone-3:hover ~ .img-4 { opacity: 1; }
    .zone-4:hover ~ .base   { opacity: 1; }


</style>

<main class="container">
    <div class="hero-logo">
        <img src="/logos/Farewell_Blu_WhiteText.gif" alt="Farewell Blu Logo" class="logo-gif" />
    </div>

    <p class="tagline"></p>

    <div class="photo-bio">
        <div class="image-swap">
            <!-- hover zones go first so they affect what comes after -->
            <div class="hover-zone zone-1"></div>
            <div class="hover-zone zone-2"></div>
            <div class="hover-zone zone-3"></div>
            <div class="hover-zone zone-4"></div>

            <img src="/images/epk/farewellblu-1.jpg" class="img base" />
            <img src="/images/epk/farewellblu-2.jpg" class="img img-2" />
            <img src="/images/epk/farewellblu-3.jpg" class="img img-3" />
            <img src="/images/epk/farewellblu-4.jpg" class="img img-4" />
        </div>


        <div class="bio">
            <p>Inspired by songwriting legends like Buddy Holly and the Beatles, Lui&rsquo;s music is a showcase of the power of strong melodies and masterful lyricism. Indelibly raw, he communicates in what feels like unprocessed overflow &mdash; relationships, frustration with the brokenness of American society, dreams for the future, and hope for better days &mdash; the words flow with genuine simplicity, leaving you feeling like you&rsquo;ve just had a conversation with a friend.</p>

            <p>&ldquo;I just sing about life,&rdquo; Lui states, simply. &ldquo;I&rsquo;m not really about being anything I&rsquo;m not &mdash; like I&rsquo;d rather just be real.&rdquo;</p>

            <p>Songs like &ldquo;I Should Be Out Dancing,&rdquo; &ldquo;You Love Me in My Dreams,&rdquo; and &ldquo;runforyourlife&rdquo; display both the unfettered sincerity and effortless melody that is Lui.</p>

            <p>In his most recent releases, Lui has evolved &mdash; bringing much of what he learned as part of The Red Leslies and other indie-rock leaning solo work to a synth-driven indie-pop sound. Effortless as always, his melodies and lyrical genuineness shine bright, marking a new artistic stage where he&rsquo;ll undoubtedly stand out.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Achievements + Listen Split Row -->
    <div class="split-section">
        <div class="achievements">
            <h2>Achievements</h2>
            <ul>
                {artist.achievements.map(item => <li>{item}</li>)}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="music">
            <h2>Top Song</h2>
            <iframe
                    src={artist.song.spotifyEmbed}
                    height="152"
                    allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
                    loading="lazy"
            ></iframe>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <div class="contact">
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${artist.contact.email}`}>{artist.contact.email}</a></p>
        <p><strong>Instagram:</strong> <a href={artist.contact.instagram}>{artist.contact.handle}</a></p>
    </div>
</main>
